{"tid":300240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】古惑仔上門拍門警告港獨人士：「我老細叫你唔好搞咁多野」","createTime":"2017-06-27T17:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T07:02:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":166,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9d0300a5dffbba1ad94204d1ba28aa0efd7b29db","tid":300240,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JangPaladin/posts/539083736434802?pnref=story\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJangPaladin%2Fposts%2F539083736434802%3Fpnref%3Dstory&d=Ldn7n4Fj2ay9UXWwZSawSsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a049ba08\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JangPaladin/posts/539083736434802?pnref=story</a><br />\n<br />\nPaladin J Jang added a photo and a video.<br />\n古惑仔上門拍門叫我收手<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/19430085_539083583101484_584299760634850046_n.jpg?oh=4f791920cae557bcf28a82f24d78e703&amp;oe=59CF7373\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F19430085_539083583101484_584299760634850046_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4f791920cae557bcf28a82f24d78e703%26oe%3D59CF7373&h=8c0cdb29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年6月27日約11:30<br />\n家中上網期間突然有人拍門兇神惡煞咁同我講:<br />\n&quot;呢度係咪XX號&quot; (明顯我係冇被點相而只係按地址找上門)<br />\n&quot;我老細叫你唔好搞咁多野&quot;<br />\n&quot;你自己做過咩心照&quot;<br />\n問佢邊範就唔肯講！<br />\n唯有著返條褲落街追佢地，<br />\n同佢地係街糾纏左一輪，<br />\n但最後搭的士走左！<br />\n片中灰衫哥哥仔誣陷我郁手郁腳，仲騷手臂畀我睇，點會丫，識我既都知我和平理性非暴力！<br />\n佢仲叫佢黑衫朋友拍片以防我郁手郁腳，唉，調轉黎咁！<br />\n落樓時報左警，等我返上黎出post阿Sir先打來問我係邊！<br />\n阿SIR話冇事毀壞又冇証據,有咩事叫我再報警喎....哦!<br />\n其實古惑仔同差佬都係打份工姐！<br />\n我點會難為大家呢？<br />\n但呢位灰衫哥哥仔態度好明顯出色過差佬！<br />\n哥哥仔幾口密，點都唔肯公開佢老闆！<br />\n同堅持兇下就算，不節外生枝！<br />\n7.1.前夕我有咩頭暈身慶都好，爬出來都會舉香港獨立旗,<br />\n大家一定堅持,推動香港獨立！"},{"pid":"cc617f37079193aa46d7044ab507594d1be1608c","tid":300240,"uid":18456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"咁誇張"},{"pid":"1779a43639d9a08a44c9ba7fbda8e95e64394198","tid":300240,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"一段時間之前有個好似係學民，收到恐嚇電話"},{"pid":"995ea22b271a7c65f1e3844901f33d4627244c6a","tid":300240,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"古惑仔會call的走佬咁破格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca898982fb568c53655d8b9e5517e4ec28cbbde4","tid":300240,"uid":41315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n小心啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf722ab4d40ccf8d953dc8d2640b19fae3fff68","tid":300240,"uid":24788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:38:43.000Z","msg":"咁嘅款  我一拳一件"},{"pid":"f040034701c81b8746bbfa7826ac40bc0a164350","tid":300240,"uid":9564,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:40:21.000Z","msg":"黑色衫嗰條友成個on9仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57d657944e9125f78c7b2c66667e4d3f6365f40","tid":300240,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"大家作好準備"},{"pid":"7531410ec849691dee693191e2cbb4ea7ea16b87","tid":300240,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁嘅款  我一拳一件</blockquote><br />\n咁就中計 即刻夾好拉你<br />\n<br />\n個款根本最有可能係警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971e564876918dcb0e9f5f0037b1c748b15a89c1","tid":300240,"uid":54223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:53:37.000Z","msg":"老闆= 警畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571ab76be2d21097eb92ae63